1. make a folder named context in a src directory
2. make a file inside that folder named UserContext.jsx
3. wrap App.jsx by Context file, inside main.jsx
4. render children element insite UserContext.jsx by giving children props
5. Create Context Provider (UserDataContext.jsx) and export it in UserContext.jsx
6. give it a value attribute (if multiple data give array)
7. If you want to access the data of that Context provider, just use useContext() and inside that bracket write the name of context provider